node.title: Ghislaine Maxwell found guilty of sex trafficking
node.content: ["\u00a0Ghislaine Maxwell, the British socialite charged with recruiting and grooming teenage girls to be sexually abused by the financier Jeffrey Epstein, has been found guilty of sex trafficking.\u00a0", "The jury in the trial reached the verdict today in the New York City courtroom, where the trial has been carried out since December.\u00a0", "This is breaking news more to come\u00a0", "\u00a0"]
